strings:
<voice_0x010012B4><se_high>*: Jessica, Jessica! Look!
I can use Transform now!
I'm not that good yet, but...

<voice_0x010012B6><se_high>*: ...Huh? That's not right!
TRANSFORM! Back to normal!

<voice_0x010012B7><se_high>*: ...Huh? That's not right either!
I've forgotten how to turn myself back!
Er... He he he!

<voice_0x010012B9><se_high>*: That's it! Phew!
I was worried I wouldn't be able to turn back!
<voice_0x010012A1><se_high>Bangerz: Jessica! I didn't know you were<endash>
<voice_0x010012A2><se_high>Jessica: Sorry Bangerz, I'm only dropping in for a bit. I've still got a long way to go.
<voice_0x010012A3><se_high>Jessica: It's a bit complicated. I've kind of avenged Alistair's death, but I kind of haven't...

<voice_0x010012A4><se_high>Bangerz: It's okay!
We're being guards until you come back!

<voice_0x010012A5><se_high>Bangerz: By the time you get back properly,
me and Mash'll be the best guards ever!
